---
title: Turkey Chiles Rellenos with Poblano Peppers and Chipotle Sauce
description: This dish is all filler, but we mean that in the best possible way. And more importantly, it’s just as satisfying on a busy weeknight as it is at a Cinco de Mayo feast. Soft-roasted poblano peppers are stuffed to the brim with a warmly spiced mix of ground turkey and rice, then blanketed with a rich tomato sauce and a layer of melted Monterey Jack cheese.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-chiles-rellenos-29fae144.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/turkey-chiles-rellenos-5aaac02030006c535c7db792-c54c9ad9.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/turkey-chiles-rellenos-5aaac02030006c535c7db792
author: Sara Heilman
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
  fat: 27 g
